reviewText:
Sadly enough most movies are unimpressive. There are a few movies with very good actors, but it seems like they are in some of their own worst movies of their careers.
Most movies in this album aren't typical gangster movies either. What you see on the box is essentially an illusion. You will hardly see a movie in this album that is depicting the image on the front of the box!
A few are gansters classics. The rest are memorabilia from old TV series. I don't recommend it for persons looking for classic movies.
This video series is a good way to reflect on the good old days when people enjoyed tasteful and suspenseful dramas and there was less real violence in the world in black and white.
Ok. Shucks!  Must write more to compete this survey. Shucks. Wish I could leave this page before writing the minimum required.
